Component Specifications\\n\\n### 3.1 Market Data Ingestion Layer\\n\\n**Respons
ibility:** Receive and parse Kalshi market data with minimal latency.\\n\\n**Des
ign Decisions:**\\n- **Primary:** WebSocket connection to Kalshi for real-time p
rice updates\\n- **Fallback:** REST polling at 100ms intervals if WebSocket drop
