al Suppression:** 500ms cooldown per pair after signal generation.\\n- **Slippag
e Guard:** Reject execution if market price moved >10bps since signal generation
.\\n\\n### 7.3 Post-Trade Safeguards\\n- **Auto-Close:** Positions automatically
