ild\n\n**Input:**\n- Your T350 architecture deep dive (`agents/public/architectu
re_deep_dive.md`)\n- Your T350 skeleton expanded (`agents/bob/backend/cpp_engine
/skeleton_expanded.cpp`)\n- Bob's correlation pairs (`agents/public/correlation_
