aker)\n7. Order router (Kalshi API, libcurl keep-alive, exponential backoff)\n8.
Position tracker (P&L, convergence monitoring, auto-close)\n\n**Performance Targ
et:**\n- End-to-end latency: <1ms (nominal ~655¬µs)\n- Throughput: >5k ticks/sec\
n- 100% code coverage on core logic\n\n**Success Criteria:**\n- [ ] Compiles cle
anly: `g++ -std=c++20 -pthread -O3`\n- [ ] All 8 components fully implemented\n-
